title: Walk On By: Humor Involved
description: Why didn’t Spiderman laugh when Ironman cracked a joke? Because he thought it was a yarn. And why didn’t Ironman laugh when Spiderman cracked a joke? Because he didn’t get the irony. ‘Walk On By’ includes many new genuine alliterative jokes, obscene jokes, sick pervert jokes, funny dialogues, witty quotations, polemics, sarcastic remarks, therapeutic notes, and myriads of punch lines about blonds, Danes, Swedes, faggots, film stars, priests, Jews, Christians, Jehovah Witnesses, republicans, democrats, cannibals, etc. Attention: This book is for adults only!
author: Stephan Attia
